{"data":[{"name":"85:1","price":"誓以有宫分的苍穹，","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡبُرُوجِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5910,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:2","price":"和所警告的日子，","arabic":"وَٱلۡيَوۡمِ ٱلۡمَوۡعُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5911,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:3","price":"以及能证的和所证的日子，","arabic":"وَشَاهِدٖ وَمَشۡهُودٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5912,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:4","price":"愿掘坑的人们，被弃绝，","arabic":"قُتِلَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡأُخۡدُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5913,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:5","price":"那坑里有燃料点着的火，","arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡوَقُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5914,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:6","price":"当时，他们坐在坑边，","arabic":"إِذۡ هُمۡ عَلَيۡهَا قُعُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5915,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:7","price":"他们见证自己对信士们的罪行，","arabic":"وَهُمۡ عَلَىٰ مَا يَفۡعَلُونَ بِٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ شُهُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5916,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:8","price":"他们对于信士们，只责备他们信仰安拉——万能的，可颂的主，","arabic":"وَمَا نَقَمُواْ مِنۡهُمۡ إِلَّآ أَن يُؤۡمِنُواْ بِٱللَّهِ ٱلۡعَزِيزِ ٱلۡحَمِيدِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5917,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:9","price":"天地的主权只是他的，安拉是见证万物的。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي لَهُۥ مُلۡكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۚ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ شَهِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5918,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:10","price":"迫害信士和信女而不悔过的人们，必受火狱的刑罚，并受火灾的惩治。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ فَتَنُواْ ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنَٰتِ ثُمَّ لَمۡ يَتُوبُواْ فَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ جَهَنَّمَ وَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ ٱلۡحَرِيقِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5919,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:11","price":"信道而且行善的人们，必入下临诸河的乐园，那确是伟大的成功。","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ جَنَّٰتٞ تَجۡرِي مِن تَحۡتِهَا ٱلۡأَنۡهَٰرُۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡفَوۡزُ ٱلۡكَبِيرُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5920,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:12","price":"你的主的惩治，确是严厉的。","arabic":"إِنَّ بَطۡشَ رَبِّكَ لَشَدِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5921,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:13","price":"他确能创造，且能再造，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ يُبۡدِئُ وَيُعِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5922,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:14","price":"他是至赦的，是至爱的，","arabic":"وَهُوَ ٱلۡغَفُورُ ٱلۡوَدُودُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5923,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:15","price":"是宝座的主，是尊严的，","arabic":"ذُو ٱلۡعَرۡشِ ٱلۡمَجِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5924,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:16","price":"是为所欲为的。","arabic":"فَعَّالٞ لِّمَا يُرِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5925,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:17","price":"你曾听见军队的故事了吗？","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡجُنُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5926,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:18","price":"法老和赛莫德人的故事。","arabic":"فِرۡعَوۡنَ وَثَمُودَ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5927,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:19","price":"不然，不信道的人们陷于否认之中，","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ فِي تَكۡذِيبٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5928,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:20","price":"安拉是从各方面包罗他们的，","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ مِن وَرَآئِهِم مُّحِيطُۢ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5929,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:21","price":"不然，这是尊严的《古兰经》，","arabic":"بَلۡ هُوَ قُرۡءَانٞ مَّجِيدٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5930,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"85:22","price":"记录在一块受保护的天牌上。","arabic":"فِي لَوۡحٖ مَّحۡفُوظِۭ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5931,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj","Chapter Al-Buruj","Buruj","Surah Buruj","Chapter Buruj","Al Buruj","Surah Al Buruj","Chapter Al Buruj","Surah 85","Chapter 85","The Constellations","البروج"]}